'''''Star Wars'': Episode I ''Racer'': Prima's Official Strategy Guide''' was a strategy guide published by [[Prima Games]] on [[June 16]], [[1999]] for the [[Wikipedia:Nintendo 64|Nintendo 64]] [[Star Wars video games|video game]] [[Star Wars: Episode I Racer|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''Racer'']]. A secondary version for [[Wikipedia:Personal computer|PC]] and [[Wikipedia:Dreamcast|Dreamcast]] was published on [[April 26]], [[2000]].

